net.sourceforge.barcodegen.print.job

Class Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.barcodegen.print.job.Job
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GenerationJob, PreviewJob, PrintJob

    public abstract class Job
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Divish on 6/14/2016. Parent class for Label Processing (e.g Print, Generation, Previuew) jobs. Holds the list of OrderPrints that need label generation Also maintains the progress of the Job in curSubJobIndex
